Interface ToDo

    @Gson.TypeAdapters
 @Value.Immutable
public interface ToDo
extends Entity
    A Todo is a container of a list of Tasks. A Todo is constructed of the tasks that need to be completed. It is combined of following properties: id : unique identity of the todo name: name of the todo created: time when a todo is created.
